Description:
    This generates a web_app_theme-based layout in app/views/layouts, copies
    the stylesheets and javascripts to public and the locales to config/locales.

Available templates:
    administration: the standard web-app-theme layout
    sign: for sign-in-pages

Available themes:
    default, amro, bec, bec-green, blue, djime-cerulean, drastic-dark,
    kathleene, olive, orange, reidb-greenish, warehouse

Example:
    rails generate web_app_theme:layout

    This will create:
        app/view/application.html.[erb|haml]

	config/locales/web_app_theme/de_de.yml
	config/locales/web_app_theme/pt_br.yml

        images/avatar.png
        images/icons/application_edit.png
        images/icons/cross.png
        images/icons/tick.png
        images/icons/key.png

        javascripts/jquery-1.3.min.js
        javascripts/jquery.scrollTo.js
        javascripts/jquery.localscroll.js

        stylesheets/base.css
        stylesheets/themes/default/style.css
        or
        stylesheets/sass/base.sass
        stylesheets/themes/default/sass/style.sass

